
# Title 22— FOREIGN RELATIONS AND INTERCOURSE
### CHAPTER 63— SUPPORT FOR EAST EUROPEAN DEMOCRACY (SEED)
#### § 5425. Use of Polish currency generated by agricultural assistance
##### (c) Commodities subject to requirements

Subsection (a) applies with respect to agricultural commodities made available for Poland for fiscal years 1990, 1991, and 1992 under section 1431(b) of title 7 , the Food for Peace Act ( 7 U.S.C. 1691 and following), and section 1736 o of title 7.
